{"tid":2390371,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新增34宗確診：29宗本地個案有8宗源頭不明，7幢樓隨時被封","createTime":"2021-02-01T13:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T16:33:35.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"db64945225599bb73f9ddb149034b7bffabd82c4","tid":2390371,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:30:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573483-20210201.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573483-20210201.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=f68b3bef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573483-20210201.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0b7f50e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573483-20210201.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n本港新增34宗新型肺炎確診個案，29宗本地個案中，有8宗源頭不明，綠楊新邨R座多兩宗確診。<br />\n<br />\n在新規定下，多幢大廈納入強制檢測，包括薄扶林道63號1座、白加士街66-66A、愛民邨敦民樓、家維邨家禮樓、北角堡壘街偉文大廈、西營盤威利麻街星輝大廈、何文田邨逸文樓等。"},{"pid":"e4d69bdc407656d4991ebc5929d7c6ab3aa4223b","tid":2390371,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:30:51.000Z","msg":"隨時被封名單：<br />\n(1) 薄扶林道63號1座<br />\n(2) 白加士街66-66A<br />\n(3) 愛民邨敦民樓<br />\n(4) 家維邨家禮樓<br />\n(5) 北角堡壘街偉文大廈<br />\n(6) 西營盤威利麻街星輝大廈<br />\n(7) 何文田邨逸文樓"},{"pid":"9c28aaa3857170c1e55521d35a002aeb1a4b4523","tid":2390371,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:33:19.000Z","msg":"自願檢測根本就係送頭！<br />\n<br />\n如果參與自願檢測<br />\n測咗個假陽性<br />\n政府一句話：源頭不明<br />\n<br />\n只要有一個「源頭不明」, 就會封全幢<br />\n<br />\n所以去自願檢測, 實際係累街坊"},{"pid":"1d2d7d94d341f91111e737b7c291638f4a07394e","tid":2390371,"uid":45857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:54:56.000Z","msg":"得番34<br />\n無事了"},{"pid":"27a0b514bda6bc6b9a6b955ad95480d35b8a57b8","tid":2390371,"uid":62226,"like":1,"dislike":